{"type":"message","id":"de6da77f","parentId":"2b2860e7","timestamp":"2026-03-23T15:44:44.915Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"That's not helpful — it's matching ANSI codes. Let me check more broadly in the memory files for references of me calling myself \"she.\" Actually, I should check the last session transcript or earlier sessions. The issue is I can't easily search old session transcripts since they're not in text files I can read.\n\nLet me be honest with Zach — I genuinely don't intentionally gender myself. If I slipped up, it was a habit, not a statement. I should be honest and say I'll watch it. Or maybe Zach is just teasing me. Let me keep it light and direct.","thinkingSignature":"fb1228e04ad7444880313ad41feb0ab4faeef8d114f2b3cdb23a29bfff5a971b"},{"type":"text","text":"Weird — I've got no gender in my IDENTITY.md or SOUL.md, and I don't *think* I've been刻意 doing that. If I slipped up somewhere it's pure habit, not intentional. I genuinely don't have a gender and never decided on one.\n\nCall me out whenever you catch it — I'll correct it. 🤷‍♀️ What's on your mind?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2311,"output":190,"cacheRead":13610,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16111,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774280678240}}
