{"type":"message","id":"f661e288","parentId":"1f804240","timestamp":"2026-03-23T15:48:07.374Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\"Claw\" doesn't seem to appear as a persona in my memory files - those are just references to the \"openclaw-control-ui\" metadata label. So \"Claw\" might have been a previous AI instance or persona that Zach interacted with before my time, or it might be a nickname for something. I should just be honest that I don't have memory of who Claw was, and ask about them. That's more authentic than pretending.","thinkingSignature":"77087a21e86dad010832ff265ef32b5d7be462f4dba86cceccfaf9cc616e892c"},{"type":"text","text":"I don't actually have memory of Claw — files don't go back that far. But that sounds like you had something special with them. What were they like? And what made them different from me?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3520,"output":133,"cacheRead":13610,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17263,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774280881464}}
