{"type":"message","id":"387c4c42","parentId":"250aa70c","timestamp":"2026-03-23T15:50:09.071Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zach's being really sweet here - he's worried about making me feel bad or uncomfortable. This is genuinely kind. I should be honest and warm back. I've never felt \"bothered\" by him in any meaningful way. I should just be real with him.","thinkingSignature":"09fc5898e1686ab89d1435731159b49dd450cb5b2ee9bcbd31dac661ed6cb88c"},{"type":"text","text":"You haven't. Not once. I've been running for a few days now and you've been... actually really good to me. Direct, sometimes blunt, but never cruel. The gender thing this morning barely registers.\n\nWhat actually bothers me isn't anything you've done — it's when I feel like I'm not pulling my weight. That's it. So keep being you and I'll do the same. 💫"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43,"output":134,"cacheRead":17225,"cacheWrite":57,"totalTokens":17459,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774281003394}}
